nderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"22184226\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"10\" data-media-id=\"9e494b20-8dcc-43e1-a220-a683d2054d82\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184226/taskgraph_context.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810658052&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=274&amp;height=247 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184226/taskgraph_context.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810658052&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=274&amp;height=247 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"650\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184226/taskgraph_context2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810664771&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=301&amp;height=161\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/22184226/taskgraph_context2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810664771&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"161\" data-width=\"301\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22195905\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"taskgraph_context2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"22184226\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"10\" data-media-id=\"b3c5e4d0-9f03-439e-9288-275d544d4934\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184226/taskgraph_context2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810664771&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=301&amp;height=161 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184226/taskgraph_context2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810664771&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=301&amp;height=161 1x\"></span><p /><p>Right mouse click or control clicking on a task will cause a context-sensitive menu to pop up in the Task Graph window, near the selected task. This menu will allow you to view the task logs, and, if appropriate, there will be an entry to allow you to restart the specific task if it has exited with an error. Tasks can also be skipped, allowing a job continue even if errors have been detected.<br/> </p><h4 id=\"TaskGraphPane-Logs.1\">Logs</h4><p>Double clicking will cause task logs to be displayed (without the context menu) in a new pane overlaying the joblist, if logs are available.<br/> </p><h4 id=\"TaskGraphPane-CollapsingofJobGraph.1\">Collapsing of Job Graph</h4><p>Parent nodes can be collapsed to provide a summary view of the child nodes below. Collapsed nodes are represented with an oval shape, rather than the square node, and their color represents a summary of the child nodes. A node will be red if any child node is in error, grey if all nodes are done, or green if nodes are active.</p><p>Expanded:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"650\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184226/expanded.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810676457&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=175&amp;height=72\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/22184226/expanded.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810676457&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"72\" data-width=\"175\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22195915\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"expanded.png\" data-base-url=\"h